{"tid":1966145,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〔幫手推上報〕港大仲推班學護去死係咪痴撚線","createTime":"2020-04-10T03:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T03:48:21.000Z","uid":198527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25e27a03e17a78fdd2d39f73a54141ea05628c5f","tid":1966145,"uid":198527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:43:58.000Z","msg":"屌聽到呢單野真係嬲撚咗，老師都唔撚錫自己班學生，仲要推佢地去死真係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家日日都廿幾單確診數字，武漢班支那人仲要開始湧緊過嚟<br />\n仲要唔知坐喺隔離個個同學有冇上過中國，接觸過確診者<br />\n一大護理系啱先出咗考試時間表，一級嘅學護有二百幾人<br />\n然後要學生每日搭車返港大<br />\n考試場所出面又唔係大，已經要百幾人迫係出面等入場考試<br />\n再一百幾人逼係考試場入面考試<br />\n一直都有學生問點解唔可以轉Online Exam？<br />\n高層<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">JANET WONG</span></span>表示，<br />\n因為Nursing係Professional degree，<br />\n所以一定要written exam，唔可以online exam<br />\n仲要話係Nursing Council規定<br />\n先唔好講港大其他professional degree都可以online exam，<br />\n點知原來理大(未fc但有人咁講)同OU(已fc)嘅nursing都已經轉哂所有考試做online exam<br />\n一係就係Janet Wong講大話，一係就係nursing council太重視一大<br />\n仲有表示六月就會如期開始出實習，所以要逼學生返考試<br />\n各位手足可唔可以推上熱門幫下手救下班學護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5BnHsp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5BnHsp.jpg&h=17cd8a49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f6562fe4af5aa746a9ab29c0bf3adf23546e40b","tid":1966145,"uid":86442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:46:02.000Z","msg":"CLS架"},{"pid":"2543ddb1b9ef94a9c05ffbe32f2df8ec572cdd23","tid":1966145,"uid":198527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f6562fe4af5aa746a9ab29c0bf3adf23546e40b","tid":1966145,"uid":86442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:46:02.000Z","msg":"CLS架"},"cite